# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok at least seven powerful bombs detonated in commuter trains and stations during the tuesday evening rush hour in bombay , india 's commercial capital , killing at least ### people and wounding close to ### .
# ::alignments
(d / detonate-01
      :ARG1 (b / bomb
            :ARG1-of (p / powerful-02)
            :quant (a / at-least
                  :op1 7))
      :location (a2 / and
            :op1 (t / train
                  :mod (p2 / person
                        :ARG0-of (c / commute-01)))
            :op2 (s / station
                  :mod p2))
      :time (h / hour
            :mod (r / rush-01)
            :time (d2 / date-entity
                  :weekday (t2 / tuesday)
                  :dayperiod (e / evening))
            :location (c2 / city
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Bombay")
                  :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91
                        :ARG1 (c3 / country
                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "India"))
                        :ARG2 (c4 / capital
                              :mod (c5 / commerce)))))
      :ARG0-of (k / kill-01
            :ARG1 (p3 / person
                  :quant (a3 / at-least
                        :op1 1000000)))
      :ARG0-of (w / wound-01
            :ARG1 (p4 / person
                  :ARG1-of (c6 / close-10
                        :ARG2 p3))))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok leaders of thailand 's anti-government protests said thursday they will surrender to police after a court dropped treason charges against them , but vowed to continue their occupation of the prime minister 's office .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :ARG0-of (l / lead-02
                  :ARG1 (p2 / protest-01
                        :ARG1 (g / government-organization
                              :ARG0-of (g2 / govern-01
                                    :ARG1 (c / country
                                          :name (n / name
                                                :op1 "Thailand"))))))
            :ARG1 (s2 / surrender-01
                  :ARG2 (p3 / police)
                  :time (d / date-entity
                        :weekday (t / thursday))
                  :time (a / after
                        :op1 (d2 / drop-05
                              :ARG0 (c2 / court)
                              :ARG1 (c3 / charge-05
                                    :ARG1 p
                                    :ARG2 (t2 / treason))
                              :prep-against p)))
            :ARG0-of s2
            :concession-of (v / vow-01
                  :ARG1 (c4 / continue-01
                        :ARG0 p
                        :ARG1 (o / occupy-01
                              :ARG0 p
                              :ARG1 (o2 / office
                                    :poss (p4 / person
                                          :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                                                :ARG2 (m / minister
                                                      :mod (p5 / prime))))))))
            :ARG0-of v))

                        :op1 "Asia"))

                        :mod (w / world))))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (m4 / monday)))

                        :ARG0-of (g3 / govern-01))

                              :quant 1000000000
                              :unit (d / dollar))))

                  :ARG1 (p5 / possible-01

            :weekday (t2 / tuesday)))

                  :time (p3 / push-01
                        :ARG0 s
                        :ARG1 (b / button)))))

                                    :ARG1-of (p3 / possible-01)))

# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (o / organization
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Medecins"
                  :op2 " sans"
                  :op3 "Frontieres")
            :mod (c / charity
                  :mod (m / medicine))
            :ARG1-of (m2 / mean-01
                  :ARG2 (d / doctor
                        :ARG0-of (h / have-03
                              :polarity -
                              :ARG1 (b / border)))))
      :ARG1 (p / possible-01
            :ARG1 (d2 / die-01
                  :ARG1 (p2 / person
                        :ARG1-of (f / free-04))
                  :frequency (r / rate-entity-91
                        :ARG3 (t / temporal-quantity
                              :quant 1
                              :unit (d3 / day)))
                  :location (r2 / region
                        :location (e / east
                              :part-of (c2 / country
                                    :name (n2 / name
                                          :op1 "Zaire"))
                              :ARG1-of (t2 / tear-01
                                    :ARG0 (s2 / strife))))))
      :medium (s3 / state-01)
      :time (d4 / date-entity
            :weekday (s4 / saturday)))

                        :mod (p2 / prime))))
      :ARG1 (o / offer-01
            :ARG1 (c / cease-01
                  :ARG1 (f / fire-01))

                  :ARG0 (p4 / person
                        :name (n2 / name

                        :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91

                                          :op1 "Palestine"))
                              :ARG2 m))))

            :weekday (s / saturday)))

# ::alignments
(h / hold-04
      :ARG0 (a / and
            :op1 (a2 / airline
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Iberia")
                  :ARG1-of (o / own-01
                        :ARG0 (s / state)))
            :op2 (p / person
                  :ARG0-of (p2 / pilot-01)
                  :ARG0-of (s2 / strike-02)))
      :ARG1 (t / talk-01
            :ARG0 a)
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (t2 / tuesday))
      :concession-of (f / fail-01
            :ARG1 a
            :ARG2 (e / end-01
                  :ARG0 a
                  :ARG1 (s3 / stoppage-01
                        :ARG1 (w / work-01)
                        :ARG0-of (c / cause-01
                              :ARG1 (d2 / disrupt-01
                                    :ARG1 (p3 / person
                                          :ARG0-of (t3 / travel-01
                                                :time (h2 / holiday
                                                      :mod (c2 / continent
                                                            :name n
                                                            :op1 "Europe"))))))))))
